1
00:00:26,916 --> 00:00:28,708
Kuniko Hojo.

2
00:00:30,708 --> 00:00:34,291
It's been three days.
You've passed the test.

3
00:00:34,375 --> 00:00:38,625
To reward your perseverance,
I will lift your burden.

4
00:00:45,916 --> 00:00:49,125
I shall end
your troublesome life.

5
