Outstanding. There's the look.

6
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:09,458
If you lay a
finger on anyone else...

7
00:01:09,541 --> 00:01:12,833
I swear to you,
they'll be the last person.

8
00:01:15,291 --> 00:01:18,750
Does anyone here wish to
take umbrage with the sentence?

9
00:01:24,833 --> 00:01:27,833
So we're all in accord as
to the fate of our firebrand?

10
00:01:27,916 --> 00:01:29,416
Excellent. Heh.

11
00:03:04,291 --> 00:03:06,541
Your update
on Digma Two, please.

12
00:03:06,625 --> 00:03:08,416
Languishing in her cell, ma'am.

13
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,750
The child's éhlan for
stirring the pot would appear

14
00:03:10,833 --> 00:03:13,666
to be spent.
At least for the time being.

15
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:17,083
Appropriately. She is condemned.

16
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:19,125
We have an alternate plan, then?

17
00:03:19,208 --> 00:03:20,583
Nothing has altered.

18
00:03:20,666 --> 00:03:23,916
If she's the sort to die,
she'd best get on with it.

19
00:03:28,166 --> 00:03:30,250
You presume to serve me Rize?!

20
00:03:30,333 --> 00:03:33,875
Is it not plain I want
Montagne Bleu san sugar?!

21
00:03:33,958 --> 00:03:35,958
I am unworthy, madam.

22
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:53,208
Good work, fellas.
We're makin' progress.

23
00:03:53,291 --> 00:03:54,625
Yes sir.

24
00:03:59,041 --> 00:04:01,416
Huh?! Son of a bitch!

25
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:09,416
We got a shit-storm!

26
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:10,583
The bastards
have slapped her with

27
