to formally sentence her first?

32
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:23,333
Ya think those Atlas thugs give
a shit about legal procedures?

33
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:26,000
Then we ought to
pickle some celery.

34
00:04:26,083 --> 00:04:28,416
The girl eats 'em
like they're going extinct.

35
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,708
And some turnips, too, I think.

36
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:34,250
You know what?
Let me handle this one.

37
00:04:36,708 --> 00:04:39,583
Jumping the
proverbial gun, as men do.

38
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:42,625
So. We jump when?

39
00:04:42,708 --> 00:04:45,458
That's really
not for us to decide.

40
00:04:46,625 --> 00:04:48,541
I suppose not.

41
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:56,166
They say
Kuniko's on death row.

42
00:04:56,250 --> 00:04:57,416
Oh, how awful!

43
00:04:57,500 --> 00:05:00,833
Surely this country's
not so far gone as that.

44
00:05:03,208 --> 00:05:04,791
Keep it together, soldier!

45
00:05:04,875 --> 00:05:07,125
How the hell else did
you expect her to end up?

46
00:05:07,208 --> 00:05:10,541
She's a damn terrorist,
not a close personal friend!

47
00:05:14,791 --> 00:05:17,583
In other news, Metal Age
ringleader Kuniko Hojo

48
00:05:17,666 --> 00:05:19,541
has been sentenced
to death for her crimes

49
00:05:19,625 --> 00:05:21,375
against the
Japanese government.

50
00:05:22,458 --> 00:05:24,791
Enough already. We get it.

51
00:05:24,875 --> 00:05:27,208
"Slow news day I guess." 

52
00:05:27,291 --> 00:05:29,708
Does the media really think
anyone's biting their nails

